metadata.name: stop the tears
metadata.description:
My name is "SADMAN" . I am a songwriter and producer from BKK, Thailand .I've been with music most of my life. And every song composing usually happens because of love.

This song is based on my real life. I started writing this song in October 2021. The lyrics refer to a woman I like. and he has taken away from me But I'm always waiting for you

I hope you like it even if it's not in your language. But music is a universal language. and hope you feel it

I still have many songs. and hope someone will like it And I'm sending in a lot of new songs.

Thanks
SADMAN'
